## 27. CLEAN GIT TREE MANDATE (Source Control Hygiene Protocol)
- **PRINCIPLE**: The Git repository is the single source of truth for all source code. It MUST be kept strictly clean — only commit code, config, and deployment scripts.
- **NO-SCREENSHOT MANDATE (CRITICAL)**: DILARANG KERAS mengambil, menyimpan, atau men-staged screenshot/media file (`.png`, `.jpg`, `.webp`, `.gif`, `.mp4`) ke dalam Git repository. Seluruh file pendukung sesi audit WAJIB dihapus sebelum task ditutup.
- **VITE HYGIENE**: DILARANG KERAS melakukan commit terhadap file temporer Vite (`vite.config.js.timestamp-*.mjs`).
- **ZERO-LEAK PROTOCOL (SECURITY)**: DLARANG KERAS melakukan commit atau push terhadap variabel atau file yang mengandung `role_key`, `service_role_key`, `secret`, `api_secret`, `jwt_secret`, atau file sensitif berekstensi `.key`, `.pem`, `.p12`, `.cert`. Segala bentuk kredensial WAJIB melalui `.env` yang ter-ignore. File dalam `tools/nexus-monitor/` WAJIB terdaftar di `.gitleaks.toml` dan `.gitignore`.
- **CLEAN UP ON SIGHT**: When a scratch file (`tmp_*.cjs`, etc.) or screenshot has served its purpose, delete it. Do not leave dead code or artifacts in the repository.
  - `contracts/` — All active Solidity smart contracts.
  - `api/` — All Vercel serverless functions.
  - `src/` — All frontend source code.
  - `scripts/` — Operational scripts divided into Atomic categories:
    - `audits/` (check_sync_status.cjs, verify-db-sync.cjs)
    - `deployments/` (initialize-cms.cjs, automated_ecosystem_deploy.cjs)
    - `sync/` (apply_migration.cjs)
    - `debug/` (monitor-server.cjs, nexus-bridge.cjs)
    - `_archive/` (legacy scripts)
  - `.agents/skills/` — Agent skill definitions and protocols.
  - `.cursorrules`, `.gitleaks.toml`, `.gitignore`, `.husky/`.
- **GIT STATUS CHECK**: Before EVERY push, the agent MUST run `git status` to visually confirm there are no unintended staged files. If the working tree is dirty with non-source files, immediately add them to `.gitignore` before proceeding.
- **CLEAN UP ON SIGHT**: When a scratch file (`tmp_*.cjs`, etc.) has served its purpose, delete it. Do not leave dead code or artifacts in the repository.

## 28. PRD HTML CONVERSION MANDATE (DOCUMENTATION ACCESSIBILITY)
- **PRINCIPLE**: All PRD updates MUST be accessible in both Markdown and HTML formats.
- **ENFORCEMENT**: Every time a PRD document (.md) in the `PRD/` folder is updated or created, the agent MUST immediately generate a corresponding HTML version using the `marked` tool (e.g., `npx marked -i version_update.md -o version_update.html`).
- **LOCATION**: The HTML version must reside in the same directory as the source Markdown file.
- **COMMIT POLICY**: Both the .md and .html versions must be committed together to ensure version parity.

## 29. AUDIT-FIRST & RE-AUDIT MANDATE (ERROR FIX PROTOCOL)

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This section is MANDATORY for EVERY error fix cycle. No exceptions.

### 29.1 Pre-Fix Audit (BEFORE touching any code)
Before fixing any error, Agent WAJIB menjalankan audit ekosistem terlebih dahulu:
```bash
# Step 1: Ecosystem Sync Audit (Mandatory Weekly: Sunday 00:00 UTC)
node scripts/audits/check_sync_status.cjs

# Step 2: Syntax Check all bundles
node -c api/user-bundle.js
node -c api/admin-bundle.js
node -c api/tasks-bundle.js

# Step 3: Zero-Hardcode Grep Scan
# grep -rn "|| [0-9]" api/ src/ --include="*.js" --include="*.jsx"
```
Jika audit menemukan **kesalahan lebih dari yang dilaporkan user**, Agent WAJIB melaporkan *semua* temuan ke user sebelum melanjutkan fix.

### 29.2 Root Cause Analysis (MANDATORY Before Code Change)
- **DILARANG KERAS** langsung menulis kode perbaikan sebelum membaca file yang relevan dan memahami root cause.
- Gunakan `grep_search` dan `view_file` untuk melacak seluruh entry point yang berkaitan dengan bug.
- Jika bug melibatkan XP/Fee/Reward, **WAJIB** periksa apakah nilai tersebut sudah diambil dari `point_settings` atau `system_settings`.
- **RELIABILITY SYNC**: Semua verifikasi sosial (Farcaster/Twitter) WAJIB menggunakan **Iterative Pagination** (Iterated Fetching) untuk mendukung user dengan following besar atau casts populer (>100 items).

### 29.3 Post-Fix Re-Audit (AFTER applying any fix)
Setelah fix diterapkan, Agent WAJIB menjalankan kembali:
```bash
# Re-run Ecosystem Sync Audit
node scripts/audits/check_sync_status.cjs

# Verify no new syntax errors introduced
node -c api/user-bundle.js
node -c api/admin-bundle.js

# Gitleaks final scan
npm run gitleaks-check
```
- Jika re-audit **LULUS** (exit code 0, ✅ ALL SYSTEMS SYNCHRONIZED): Task dinyatakan selesai.
- Jika re-audit **GAGAL**: Agent DILARANG menutup task atau melakukan `git push`. Perbaiki error baru terlebih dahulu dan ulangi siklus ini dari **29.1**.

### 29.4 The Fix Cycle (Lua Loop)
```
Error Dilaporkan / Weekly Schedule (Sunday 00:00 UTC)
  └─► 29.1: Pre-Fix Audit  ──[Temuan Baru?]──► Report ke User (node scripts/audits/check_sync_status.cjs)
        └─► 29.2: Root Cause Analysis
              └─► Implementasi Fix
                    └─► 29.3: Re-Audit
                          ├─[PASS]──► Notify User & git commit
                          └─[FAIL]──► Kembali ke 29.1
```

### 29.5 Dokumentasi Hasil Audit (REPORTING STANDARD v3.24.0)
Setiap hasil re-audit wajib disertakan dalam pesan notifikasi ke user dengan format:
```
✅ VERDICT: [STATUS] (Operational / Degraded)
📡 Pipeline: [FUNCTIONAL / DEGRADED] (Data Flow Integrity)
🛡️  Security Matrix: [X] checks PASSED (Gitleaks & Secret Mandate)
```

### 29.6 SURGICAL FIX MANDATE (ANTI-DESTRUCTION CODE)
- **PRINSIP**: Jika memperbaiki error, **DILARANG KERAS** menghapus seluruh blok kode atau mengganti seluruh file dengan kode yang baru.
- **EKSEKUSI**: Hanya hapus dan ganti baris atau blok kode yang spesifik menjadi penyebab error (Surgical Fix).
- **TUJUAN**: Menjaga integritas logika bisnis yang sudah ada dan meminimalkan regresi yang tidak perlu.

## 30. DEFENSIVE ADDRESS CLEANING MANDATE (NEW)
- **ZERO TOLERANCE FOR MALFORMED ADDRESSES**: Every contract address fetched from environment variables MUST be sanitized to remove accidental quotes (`"`, `'`), spaces, and hidden characters (`\r\n`).
- **FRONTEND ENFORCEMENT**: `contracts.js` must implement a `cleanAddr` utility and apply it to all `getAddr` calls.
- **SECURITY IMPACT**: This prevents "Gas Estimation Failed" errors caused by invalid address strings during web3 interactions.
- **AUDIT CHECK**: Verify that no address used in `publicClient` or `walletClient` contains leading/trailing non-hex characters.

## 31. MULTI-PROJECT VERCEL SYNC MANDATE (NEW)
Contract addresses **MUST** be synchronized across all associated Vercel projects using Vercel CLI.
- **Scope**: `crypto-discovery-app`, `dailyapp-verification-server`.
- **Targets**: Production (Mainnet), Preview (Sepolia), Development (Sepolia).
- **Required Action**: `vercel env rm` -> `vercel env add` for all targets on both projects.

## 32. ATOMIC SCRIPT ORGANIZATION MANDATE (v3.24.0)
- **PRINCIPLE**: Chaotic root script directories are prohibited.
- **ENFORCEMENT**: All operational scripts MUST reside in categorized sub-folders within `scripts/`.
- **CATEGORIES**: `audits/`, `deployments/`, `sync/`, `debug/`, `_archive/`.
- **PORTABILITY**: Every script MUST use `path.join(__dirname, ...)` for relative asset/bridge resolution to ensure functionality regardless of its location in the hierarchy.

## 33. PROFILE & CHARACTER LIMITS MANDATE (v3.24.0)
- **ENFORCEMENT**: All profile update logic MUST strictly enforce:
  - `MAX_NAME_LEN`: 50 chars.
  - `MAX_BIO_LEN`: 160 chars.
  - `MAX_USERNAME_LEN`: 30 chars.
  - `MAX_AVATAR_BYTES`: 1,048,576 bytes (1MB).
- **FALLBACK**: Use `parseInt(process.env.VAR || 'DEFAULT')` for all limit values.

## 34. STREAK & CLAIM WINDOW MANDATE
- **STREAK WINDOW**: Claims must fall between 20 hours (`STREAK_WINDOW_MIN_HOURS`) and 48 hours (`STREAK_WINDOW_MAX_HOURS`) to increment the streak.
- **ZERO MAGIC**: These numbers MUST NOT be hardcoded in `user-bundle.js` or elsewhere.


## 35. ADMIN SYNC MANDATE (v3.24.0)
- **ENFORCEMENT**: Every administrative action on-chain (Token Whitelist, SBT Upgrade) MUST be synchronized with the database immediately upon transaction confirmation via a signed secure request to the backend. No state drift between Contract and Database is permitted.

## 36. SCHEMA IMMUTABLE PROTECTION MANDATE (v3.24.0)
- **ANTI-DELETION**: The `last_seen_at` column in the `user_profiles` table is a CRITICAL component for XP Sync API and the Anti-Whale Underdog Catch-up logic.
- **ENFORCEMENT**: 🚨 NEVER delete, rename, or modify the `last_seen_at` column, nor any other vital schema columns governing rewards without explicit A-D-R-R-E cycles. Deleting this column breaks the ecosystem's leaderboard synchronization process.

## 37. ECOSYSTEM DOCUMENTATION & SURGICAL CHANGE MANDATE (v3.26.1)
- **No-Lost-Agent Breach**: Dilarang melakukan pencarian file manual (explorative `list_dir`) tanpa memeriksa [WORKSPACE_MAP.md](file:///e:/Disco%20Gacha/Disco_DailyApp/.agents/WORKSPACE_MAP.md) terlebih dahulu. Mandat navigasi ini WAJIB dijalankan ulang setiap kali `> re-read skills` diaktifkan.
- **CONTINUOUS DOC SYNC**: Setiap kali Agent melakukan perubahan pada struktur folder (tambah/pindah file) atau fitur inti, Agent **WAJIB** memperbarui `.agents/WORKSPACE_MAP.md` dan `PRD/DISCO_DAILY_MASTER_PRD.md` secara harian.
- **SURGICAL DOCUMENTATION**: DILARANG hanya mengganti kode tanpa penjelasan. Setiap implementasi fix atau fitur baru wajib menyertakan:
  1. **Rationale**: Mengapa kode lama diubah (Root Cause).
  2. **Function**: Apa kegunaan kode baru ini.
  3. **Audit Verdict**: Hasil audit (`check_sync_status.cjs`) setelah perubahan.
- **NO DELETION WITHOUT TRACE**: Dilarang menghapus logika lama yang masih berfungsi. Gunakan pendekatan "Surgical Fix" (hanya ubah baris yang error) dan berikan komentar penjelasan di atas blok kode yang diubah jika kompleksitasnya tinggi.

